item.g:title: Maize Yellow Lycra Cotton Readymade Casual Stretch Jeggings
item.g:description: Maize Yellow mid-rise jeggings has an elasticated waistband, scoop pocket on the both side of the front waist embellished with buttons, two patch pockets on the back and tapered legs.Team it with a top/tunic/casual T-shirt and a pair of heels or flats to make a fashion statement.There might be some color variation.
